snippet.title: Dhurandhar First Look | Ranveer Singh | Aditya Dhar | In Cinemas 5th December 2025
snippet.description:
Uncover the story of unknown men and their unstoppable fight! 

#Dhurandhar – First look out now.
In Cinemas 5th December 2025.

Jio Studios Presents
A B62 Studios Production

An Aditya Dhar Film
DHURANDHAR

Written, Directed and Produced by: Aditya Dhar
Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced by: Lokesh Dhar

Cast:  Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna | R. Madhavan | Arjun Rampal | Sara Arjun

First Look Asset BGM by Shashwat Sachdev 
Orignal Song Name: Na De Dil Pardesi Nu (Jogi)
Music: Shashwat Sachdev, Charanjit Ahuja
Rap: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas
Singers: Mohd. Sadiq, Ranjit Kaur, Jasmine Sandlas, Sudhir Yaduvanshi
Lyrics: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Babu Singh Maan

Cinematography: Vikash Nowlakha 
Executive Producer: Rahul H. Gandhi 
Editor: Shivkumar V. Panicker
Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA
Character and Prosthetics Designer: Preetisheel Singh DSouza 
Production Designer: Saini S. Johray 
Sound Designer: Bishwadeep Chatterjee 
Costume Designer: Smriti Chauhan 
Action Directors: Aejaz Gulab, Sea Young Oh, Yannick Ben, Ramazan Bulut 
Music and Background Score: Shashwat Sachdev 
Lyrics: Kumaar 
Choreographer: Vijay Ganguly
Associate Director & Second Unit Director: Rohun Rege 
Chief Assistant Director: Sameer Sadhwani 
Line Producer: Naseer Ahmed Khan
Director’s Assistant: Ojas Gautam
Creative Producer: Aarsh Vora
Assistant Producer: Shweta Vora 
Consultant: Aditya Raj Kaul 
Associate Editor: Juhii Gopalakishnan 
Sound Recordist: Manas Bal 
Post Producer: Gautamik  
Re-Recording Mixer: Justin Jose K (CAS)
VFX Supervisor (Shoot): Vishal Kapoor, Dhruti Ranjan Sahoo (Philm CGI) 
VFX Studios: Philm CGI, Envision VFX 
DI Studio: Prime Focus Ltd. 
DI Colourist: Ashirwad Hadkar 
Marketing Director: Max Marketing Ltd. 
PR Agency: Communique Film PR 
Digital Agency : White Rivers Media
Publicity Design: Anil and Bhanu 
Visual Promotions: Just Right Studioz NX 
Music Label: Saregama

snippet.title: KINGDOM Release Date Promo | Vijay Deverakonda | Anirudh Ravichander | Naga Vamsi | Gowtam Tinnanuri
snippet.description:
#KINGDOM~ Starring Vijay Deverakonda in Lead Role. Directed by Gowtam Tinnanuri. Music by Anirudh Ravichander. Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya Under Sithara Entertainments & Fortune 4 Cinemas Banner. Presented by Srikara Studios.

#Kingdom will roar in theatres Worldwide on July 31st! 👊🏾

Starring: Vijay Deverakonda, Satyadev, Bhagyashri Borse and Others

Crew Details:

Written & Directed By: Gowtam Tinnanuri 
Produced By: Naga Vamsi S – Sai Soujanya 
Music Composed By: Anirudh Ravichander
Cinematography: Jomon T John ISC, Girish Gangadharan ISC
Editor: Navin Nooli
Production Designer: Avinash Kolla
Costume Designer: Neeraja Kona
Song Choreographer: Dar Gai, Vijay Binni
Action Choreographer’s: Yannick Ben, Chethan D’Souza, Real Satish
Colorist: Ranga (Prasad Studio)
Sound Design: Sync Cinema
VFX Supervisor:  Vasudeva Rao M 
Co – Director: Sri Vastav 
Production Team: Girish Dasika, Uma Mahesh Karumanchi 
Audio on Aditya Music

Chief Associate Director: Basheer
Associate Directors: B.V. Raveendra, Tirumala Reddy Akki, Muthayam Vijay Kumar, Mahesh Talluri, Geetha Sapuru & Nallandula Jagadeesh
Assistant Directors: Manoj Rishie, MS Vihari, Shrikaran Beecharaju, Akhil Raj & Parth Bane
Online Editor: Santosh Kiran 
Publicity Design: Working Tittle (A Siva Kiran)
Still Photography: Prem
A Sithara Entertainments Production
in Association with Fortune Four Studios
Presented by Srikara Studios

শুনুন দেব-শুভশ্রী অভিনীত নতুন ছবি, ধুমকেতু থেকে অরিজিৎ সিং ও শ্রেয়া ঘোষালের কন্ঠে ও অনুপম রায়ের সঙ্গীত পরিচালনায় নতুন গান, "গানে গানে"

Get ready to be swept away by the magic of music with "Gaane Gaane", a heartwarming romantic track that blends soulful vocals with mesmerizing visuals. Featuring the stellar duo Dev and Subhashree, this song beautifully captures love, nostalgia, and emotion – brought to life by the magical voices of Arijit Singh and Shreya Ghoshal.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4443: Chakori Ka Saamna
------------------------------------------------------------
The colony members find themselves trapped in the bungalow while Chakori starts scaring them with her tricks. How will they survive this spooky night?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4443 | 7 July 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the full episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090484595

Kunjungi ecb.co.uk untuk bergabung dengan We Are England Cricket Supporters secara gratis dan dapatkan akses prioritas ke tiket dan banyak lagi!

Saksikan cuplikan pertandingan dari Hari ke-5 Tes Rothesay antara Inggris dan India di Edgbaston, Birmingham

Ini adalah saluran resmi ECB. Saksikan semua video terbaru dari tim Kriket Inggris dan Dewan Kriket Inggris dan Wales, termasuk cuplikan, wawancara, dan fitur yang akan membuat Anda lebih dekat dengan tim Inggris dan pemain daerah.

Berlangganan untuk informasi selengkapnya: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

Menampilkan video dari tim kriket Inggris, Vitality Blast, Kejuaraan Daerah, Piala Satu Hari Metro Bank, dan banyak lagi.

hi.title: दीप ने छक्का जड़कर भारत को एजबेस्टन में जीत दिलाई! | हाइलाइट्स - इंग्लैंड बनाम भारत दिन 5 | रोथेस...
hi.description:
ecb.co.uk पर जाकर We Are England Cricket Supporters से निःशुल्क जुड़ें और टिकट तथा अन्य बहुत सी चीज़ों पर प्राथमिकता प्राप्त करें!

बर्मिंघम के एजबेस्टन में इंग्लैंड और भारत के बीच रोथेसे टेस्ट के 5वें दिन के मैच हाइलाइट्स देखें

यह ECB का आधिकारिक चैनल है। इंग्लैंड क्रिकेट टीमों और इंग्लैंड और वेल्स क्रिकेट बोर्ड के सभी नवीनतम वीडियो देखें, जिसमें हाइलाइट्स, साक्षात्कार और इंग्लैंड टीमों और काउंटी खिलाड़ियों के बारे में आपको और करीब लाने वाली विशेषताएँ शामिल हैं।

अधिक जानकारी के लिए सदस्यता लें: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

इंग्लैंड क्रिकेट टीमों, विटैलिटी ब्लास्ट, काउंटी चैम्पियनशिप, मेट्रो बैंक वन-डे कप और बहुत कुछ के वीडियो शामिल हैं।

ko.title: 딥 테이크 식스, 인도 에지바스턴 원정 승리! | 하이라이트 - 잉글랜드 vs 인도 5일차 | 로데세이 테스트 2025
ko.description:
ecb.co.uk에서 We Are England Cricket Supporters에 무료로 가입하고 티켓 우선 구매 등 다양한 혜택을 누리세요!

버밍엄 에지바스턴에서 열린 로데세이 테스트 5일차 잉글랜드와 인도의 경기 하이라이트를 시청하세요.

ECB 공식 채널입니다. 잉글랜드 크리켓 팀과 잉글랜드 웨일즈 크리켓 위원회의 최신 영상을 모두 시청하세요. 하이라이트, 인터뷰, 특집 기사를 통해 잉글랜드 팀과 카운티 선수들을 더욱 가까이에서 만나볼 수 있습니다.

더 많은 정보를 원하시면 구독하세요: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

잉글랜드 크리켓 팀, 바이탈리티 블라스트, 카운티 챔피언십, 메트로 뱅크 원데이 컵 등의 영상을 제공합니다.

de-DE.title: Deep holt sechs Siege für Indien in Edgbaston! | Highlights – England gegen Indien, Tag 5 | Rothe...
de-DE.description:
Besuchen Sie ecb.co.uk und werden Sie kostenlos Mitglied bei We Are England Cricket Supporters. Sie erhalten bevorzugten Zugang zu Tickets und vielem mehr!

Sehen Sie sich die Spielhighlights vom 5. Tag des Rothesay-Tests zwischen England und Indien in Edgbaston, Birmingham, an.

Dies ist der offizielle Kanal des ECB. Sehen Sie sich die neuesten Videos der englischen Cricket-Teams und des England and Wales Cricket Board an, darunter Highlights, Interviews und Reportagen, die Ihnen die englischen Teams und County-Spieler näherbringen.

Abonnieren Sie für mehr: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

Mit Videos der englischen Cricket-Teams, des Vitality Blast, der County Championship, des Metro Bank One-Day Cup und mehr.

snippet.title: Namit Malhotra's Ramayana: The Introduction | Nitesh Tiwari | Ranbir, Yash, Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman
snippet.description:
An outcome through a collaboration of some of the world’s best to ensure that Ramayana is presented with the greatest amount of Reverence and Respect. 

Welcome to the Beginning. 

Let’s celebrate the IMMORTAL story of Rama v/s Ravana. 

Our Truth. Our History.

Directed by Nitesh Tiwari, Produced by Namit Malhotra’s Prime Focus Studios and 8-time Oscar winning VFX studio DNEG in association with Yash’s Monster Mind Creations; Ramayana is being filmed for IMAX and will release worldwide: Part 1 on Diwali 2026 and Part 2 on Diwali 2027.

Namit Malhotra’s Ramayana

Starring:
Ranbir Kapoor as Rama
Yash as Ravana
Sai Pallavi as Sita
Ravie Dubey as Lakshman
Sunny Deol as Hanuman

Co-Produced by Yash
Written by Shridhar Raghavan
Directed by Nitesh Tiwari

Music by Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman
Lyrics by Kumar Vishwas

VFX by DNEG (8-time Academy Award winners)

Filmed for IMAX

Presented by Prime Focus Studios in association with Monster Mind Creations

🛕 This journey to Puri Yatra sets the tone for a spiritual and comic adventure like never before. Don’t miss this laugh-packed ride!

snippet.title: Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

As new deadly games return, Arisu, Usagi and new players must navigate even more daunting, adrenaline-fueled challenges.

snippet.description:

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi

snippet.title: Blessed With Baby Boy Allhamdullilah👶🏻❤️ | Adnaan 07
snippet.description:
Today, my life changed forever.
I became a father and Alhamdulillah, it’s a baby boy.

The moment I heard his first cry, something inside me shifted. A love I never knew existed was born. It’s hard to put into words what it feels like, but I tried capturing every moment, every emotion, and every heartbeat.

This video holds one of the most precious memories of my life. The arrival of my son. The nervousness, the joy, the tears, and the silent prayers.

Thank you for being a part of this journey. Your love and duas mean more than words can ever say.

This is the beginning of something truly beautiful. Do remember us in your prayers.✨

#FathersLove #BabyBoy #Adnaan07 #AdnaanShaikh

snippet.description:

Singer: Gopal Bharwad, Manisha Bharwad
Artists: Chhaya Thakor, Kuldeep Mishra
Music: Jackie Gajjar
Lyrics: RK Thakor
Recording: Sargam Studio - Patan

Producer: Gunvant Thakor

Ho Lai Ja Ne Lerida Tara
Ho Lai Ja Ne Lerida Tara Nehade Javu Re
Ho Lal Odhu Mathe Odhani Tari Hel Ma Aavu Re
Ho Bangala Tara Paka Paya Na
Bangala Tara Paka Paya Na Kachi Mati Na Ghar
Naliya Na Thekana Nathi Kem Lai Javu Malak
Ho Lai Ja Ne Lerida Tara Nehade Javu Re

Ho Nanu Ek Zupadu Maru, Man Lagi Nai Taru
Sukh Sahebi Ma Mohya, Oy Ro To Haru
Ho Ho Ho Bangala Ni Mediye, Man Nathi Mohya
Vari Bethi Tamne Valam Jyarthi Me To Joya
Ho Halti Chatak Harni Ni Jem
Halati Chatak Harani Ni Jem, Harnya Halar Desh
Pag Ma Vagashe Kankariyu Tane Kem Hamjavu Re
Ho Lai Ja Ne Valam Tara Malak Ma Javu Re

Ho Prem Niswarth Taro, Bharoho Te Jityo Maro
Ek Bija Na Thaine Jivashu Aa Janmaro
Ho Ho Ho Haiya Na Re Het Aato, Khoti Nai Thay Vato
Saath Nai Chhodu Valam Jiv Bhale Jato
Ho Bar Medi Na Bangala Mare
Bar Medi Na Bangala, An Bangale Melya Madh
Hona Na Moraliya Bole Halo Mare Desh
Ae Halo Ne Hangath Lerida Deh Ma Jashu Re

snippet.description:
Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

ta.title: உலகின் மிக வேகமான கார் vs சிறுத்தை!

snippet.description:
सिर्फ चावल का बनाएं झटपट बनने वाला राइस ढोकला, स्पंजी, हेल्दी -स्वादिष्ट व इतना नरम मुंह में जाते ही घुल जाए, Easy Rice Dhokla Recipe–Light and Healthy Steamed Breakfast
#dhokla #breakfast #nashta 
Ingredients for Rice Dhokla
चावल का आटा - Rice flour - 1 cup (140 grams)
दही - Curd - 1 cup
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
पिसी चीनी - Sugar powder - 1 tsp
ईनो - Eno - 1 tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 2 no
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves - 15-20 no

snippet.title: Kajal Maheriya | Kudrat 2.0 | કાજલ મહેરીયા |  કુદરત 2.0 | New Gujarati Sad Song 2025
snippet.description:
જિગ્નેશ બારોટના સુપરહિટ ગીત "કુદરત" નો નવો અંદાજ! હવે સાંભળો કુદરત 2.0 કાજલ મહેરીયા ની મીઠી અવાજમાં માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati પર! ❤️🎶

Credits:
Singer: Kajal Maheriya
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Lyrics: Darshan Bajigar
Music:  Ravi Nagar & Rahul Nadiya
Production: BorisanaWala Film Production 
Artist: Samarth Sharma, Chhaya Thakor
Co.Artist: Bharat Chaudhary, Babusinh Thakor
Creative Producer: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support:  Jenish Talaviya
Crowd: Sanjay
DOP: Atul Thakor
Editing: Kishor  Rajaput
DI: AU Studio
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Assi. Di.: Babisinh Thakor
Makeup Team: Harshad Sharma & Team
Spot:  Sandip Vaja, Ishan Parmar 
Poster Design: Aman Agola
Costume: M.M Dresswala 
Special Thanks:  Sanjay Bambhaniya, Pratik Jadav
Travel: Kanu Thakor \, Rudra Mahakal

Lyrics:
હો  દિલ નું કેઉ માનું તો દુનિયા નડે છે 
હો  દિલ નું કેઉ માનુતો દુનિયા નડે છે
લોહી ના આંસુ  મારી આંખો રડે છે ...(.2.)
 તું મને ના ..મળી.. હું તને ના મળ્યો 
 તને મને જુદા કરી કુદરત રડ્યો....
 હો દિલ નું કેઉ માનુતો દુનિયા નડે છે
  લોહી ના આંસુ  મારી આંખો રડે છે ...
  હો લઈ જા ને યાદ મારી હાચવીને રાખજે
  મારી મોહોબત ને હમભાળી રાખજે 
  અરે તારો વિશ્વાસ કર્યો હદ થી વધારે ..
   કુદરત જાણે હવે મળશું પાછા ક્યારે....
   હું તારી યાદ મા રોઝ મરતો રહું
   તને યાદ કરી  જાન જીવતો રહું
   હો  દિલ નું કેઉ માનુ તો દુનિયા નડે છે 
   લોહી ના આંસુ આખો રડે છે
   ઓ ફૂલ થી સજેલો મારો બાગ કરમાંણો.....(2)
   તારા રે  કારણે મારો પ્રેમ વગોવાણો
   રોજ તને યાદ કરી રાત વીતી જાશે.... 
   તારી યાદો માં મારી જિંદગી પુરી થાશે 
   તું મને ના મળી  હું તને ના મળ્યો
   તને મને જુદા કરી કુદરત રડ્યો
   કાજલ ના  દિલ નું કેઉ માનું તો દુનિયા નડે છે
   લોહીના આસુ  મારી  આખો રડે છે

snippet.title: Headlights - Udta Jaaye @alok (ft. @KRSNAOfficial & @RashmeetKaur ) | Free Fire MAX
snippet.description:
When DJ Alok touched down in India, we knew we had to cook up a banger 💥
With your favorites @KRSNAOfficial and @RashmeetKaur on the track...we turned the heat all the way up 🔥🎶

SONG LYRICS:

Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
O-Ohhh junoon har saans mein,
O-Ohhh hatheli par hai jaan,
O-Ohhh tum hi rakho zameen,
O-Ohhh mera hai aasmaan.

Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Haan ye dil Udta Jaaye, poochho na ye kahaan jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Ab to ye Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.
Haan ye dil Udta Jaaye, poochho na ye kahaan jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.

Dekho aaj bhi main ladoon jaise kuchh nahi hai khone ko,
Kone kone mein jaane log, ab poochhe na kaun hai woh.
Itne sapne dekhe toh milta nahi hai sone ko,
Iss game mein top brass, ye peetal bolenge sone ko.
Bole kaam kar, maine kare kaam fir,
Hota na pareshan, meri lage jaan fir,
Subah chale shaam, chale sar-e-aam fir,
Jab kalam se chale chaal, bane kalamkaar fir.

오-오오 오늘을 살아야지, 오-오오 그래, 난 근심 없어.

호-오오 하늘에 불이 있어, 호-토 사는 재미가 있어,
오-아아 매 순간이 인생이야, 오-아아 우리는 최대한 살 거야.

이제 날아갈 거야, 내 심장이 날아갈 거야,

원하는 건 뭐든 얻을 거야, 목적 없이 날아갈 거야.

그래, 내 심장이 날아갈 거야, 어디로 갈지 묻지 마,

원하는 건 뭐든 얻을 거야, 목적 없이 날아갈 거야.

어두운 밤이었어,

꿈도 꿨어,

그래, 낮에 힘든 걸 봤어,

밤도 봤어.

난 이런 인내심 없어,

나보다 더 열심히 일하는 사람이 누구야?

난 할 수 있는 기술이 있어,

적 분대를 죽이거나 쓸어버릴 수 있는.

난 - 부야!

네 크루에게 가,

누구 친구야?

난 널 전혀 몰랐으니까.

난 널 전혀 몰랐으니까.

움직이고 있어,
같이 약탈하자,
하지만 넌 여전히 풋내기처럼 보여,
내가 뚫고 나가니까.
노래하고 있어…

이제 내 심장이 날아올라, 내 심장이 날아올라,
내가 원하는 건 뭐든 갖게 해 줘, 날게 해 줘.

그래, 내 심장이 날아올라, 어디로 가는지 묻지 마,
내가 원하는 건 뭐든 갖게 해 줘, 날게 해 줘.

pl.title: Reflektory — Udta Jaaye @alok (z udziałem @KRSNAOfficial i @RashmeetKaur ) | Bezpłatny ogień MAX
pl.description:
Kiedy DJ Alok wylądował w Indiach, wiedzieliśmy, że musimy przygotować bangera 💥
Z Twoimi ulubieńcami @KRSNAOfficial i @RashmeetKaur na torze... podkręciliśmy atmosferę na całego 🔥🎶

TEKST PIOSENKI:

Ab do ciebie Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.

O-ohh junoon har saans mein,
O-ohhhatheli par hai jaan,
O-ohhh tu cześć rakho zameen,
O-ohh mera hai aasmaan.

Ab do ciebie Udta Jaaye, dil mera Udta Jaaye,
Jo chahe woh paa jaaye, awara Udta Jaaye.

Tak, moje serce leci, nie pytaj dokąd ma lecieć,
Niech znajdzie się cokolwiek chcę, niech odleci.
Teraz leci, moje serce leci,
Niech znajdzie się cokolwiek chcę, niech odleci.
Tak, moje serce leci, nie pytaj dokąd ma lecieć,
Niech znajdzie się cokolwiek chcę, niech odleci.

Patrz, nawet dziś jestem głupcem, nie ma nic do stracenia,
Ludzie idą w różne kąty, teraz pytają kim jest.
Nie mogę zasnąć, nawet po tylu snach,
W tej grze jestem szefem, ci ludzie powiedzą złoto.

Pozwól mi pracować, będę pracować,
Nie będę się martwić, znów poczuję się dobrze,
Chodźmy rano, chodźmy wieczorem, stańmy twarzą w twarz,
Kiedy pióro się poruszy, znów staniemy się pisarzami.

O-Ohhh każda chwila jest ostatnia, O-Ohhh jakie są wieści o jutrze,
O-Ohhh muszę żyć dziś, O-Ohhh tak, jestem beztroski.

Ho-Ooo jest ogień na niebie, Ho-Toh jest zabawa w życiu,
O-Aaa każda chwila jest życiem, Oo-Aaa będziemy żyć w pełni.

Teraz będzie latać, moje serce będzie latać,

Dostanę wszystko, czego chcę, będę latać bez celu.

Tak, moje serce będzie latać, nie pytaj mnie, dokąd poleci,

Dostanę wszystko, czego chcę, będę latać bez celu.

Była ciemna noc,

Widziałem też sny,

Tak, widziałem trudności w ciągu dnia,

Widziałem też noc.

Nie mam takiego poziomu cierpliwości,

Kto jest bardziej pracowity ode mnie?

Mam umiejętności, aby

Zabić lub zniszczyć oddział wroga.

Mówię - Booyah!

Idź do swojej załogi,

Kim jesteś, przyjacielu?

Bo nigdy cię nie znałem.

Bo nigdy cię nie znałem.

Ruszam się,
Zbierajmy łupy razem,
Ale nadal wyglądasz jak nowicjusz,
Bo strzelam.
Śpiewam…

Teraz moje serce leci, moje serce leci,
Pozwól mi zdobyć cokolwiek chcę, pozwól mi latać.

Tak, moje serce leci, nie pytaj mnie, dokąd idzie,
Pozwól mi zdobyć cokolwiek chcę, pozwól mi latać.

,

snippet.title: Aa Samiya - Hansraj Raghuwanshi | Himachali Song | शिव  नुआला: Sawan Special Bhole Baba Song
snippet.description:
Aa Samiya - Hansraj Raghuwanshi | Himachali Song | Official Video | Sawan Special Bhole Baba Song 
#aasamiya #hansrajraghuwanshi #shivbhajan #himachalisong
__________
"Aa Samiya"  | शिव  नुआला:  
यह कोई साधारण गीत नहीं, बल्कि भगवान शिव को समर्पित एक लोक गायन परंपरा का हिस्सा है, जो हिमाचल प्रदेश के गद्दी समुदाय से जुड़ी है।

जब किसी की मनोकामना पूरी होती है, जब घर में कोई विशेष खुशी या उत्सव होता है, तब गद्दी लोग अपने आराध्य भगवान शिव को धन्यवाद देने हेतु, नुआला लोक उत्सव का आयोजन करते हैं।

यह उत्सव पूरी रात चलता है, जिसमें भगवान शिव की स्तुति, लोक भजन, और भक्ति की गूंज सुनाई देती है।
इसमें भगवान शिव से प्रार्थना की जाती है —
"भूखे को अन्न, प्यासे को पानी, अंधे को आंखें दो... और इस दुनिया का कल्याण कीजिए।"

अगर आपने आज तक कोई नुआला नहीं सुना,
तो "Aa Samiya" से शुरुआत करें।
 यह गीत नहीं, भगवान शिव से जुड़ने का मार्ग।
__________

Lyrics : 
Rowdy Rhymes Lyrics

ಬನ್ನಿ ಎಲ್ಲಾ gangster ಮಕ್ಕಳೇ 
ಇಂದಿನ ರೌಡಿ ರೈಮ್ಸ್ ಸ್ಪೆಷಲ್ ಕ್ಲಾಸ್ನ ಶುರು ಮಾಡಣ 
ರೌಡಿ ರೈಮ್ಸ್ 

 a for ಅಡ್ಡ 
ನಕ್ಕನ್ ಅಡ್ಡಕ್ ಬಾ ನೋಡ್ಕೋತಿನಿ 

b for ಬ್ಲೇಡು 
ಲೇ ಎಳೆದ್ರೆ ಹೋಗ್ಬುಡ್ತಿಯ, ಬೇಕಾ ಇವೆಲ್ಲಾ? 

c for ಚಮಕ್ಕು 
ಬೇಡ ಮರಿ lookuuuu

d for dealingsuuu
no pheelingsuuu

ಲೇ ಚಿನ್ನ
ಇಲ್ಲಿ ಯಾರು ಬಂದು ಮೇಲೆತ್ತಲ್ಲ ನಿನ್ನ 
ಗುನ್ನ ಕೊಟ್ರೇನೆ ಇಲ್ಲಿ ನಿಂಗೆ ಅನ್ನ 
ಬೇರೆ ಮಾತೆ ಇಲ್ಲ ಸೀದಾ ನುಗ್ಗು 
ಫುಲ್ ಟೈಮ್ baddie 
i am a ding dong daddy ಲೇ

full dealingsuuu
no pheelingsuuu
only dealingsu 

e for ಎಗ್ರು
ಯೇ ಓಡ್ತಾ ಇರು 
ಕುರುಪ್ ಹಾಕ್ಬುಡ್ತಿನಿ 

f for figure-u
ಮಚ್ಚ ನಿನ್ ಹಳೆ ಡವ್ ಬಂದ್ಲೋ 

g for ಗುಬಾಲ್ 
ನಮ್ ಏರಿಯಾದ ವಿಶೇಷವಾದ ಗುಬಾಲ್ ಈ ನನ್ ಮಗಾನೆ 

h for ಹವಾಲಾ 
life ಜಿಂಗಾಲಾಲ

i for ಇಕ್ಕು 
j for ಜಂಡು 
k  ಕರಾಬು 
l for ಲೋಪರ್ 
m for ಮಾಂಜಾ 
n for njaaaay 
o for ಓಂ 
p ಫಾರ್ ಪುಡಾಂಗು

q for ಕ್ವಾರ್ಟರ್-u 
ಉಯ್ಯೋ ಸ್ವಲ್ಪ wateruuu

r for ರೆಸ್ಪೆಕ್ಟ್-u 
ಮಾಡ್ಲೇಬೇಡ expect-u

s for ಸುಪಾರಿ
ಎತ್ತಿ ಬಿಡ್ರೋಲೇ

T for ತುಕಾಲಿ 
ಪಾಪ ಬಿಡ್ರೋಲೇ 

U for ಊರ್ಮಿಳಾ 
Sweettt Dreamzzz
V for ವಾಂಚು 

W for ವಾರೆಂಟ್-u 
ಏರೋಪ್ಲೇನ್ ಮೇ ಚಪಾತಿ ಕರೆಗಾ ರೇ 

X for ಜೆರಾಕ್ಸ್-ಉ 
ಸೈಕಲ್ ಗ್ಯಾಪ್ ಅಲ್ಲಿ ಆಟೋ ಓಡಿಸಿಬಿಟ್ಟವ್ನೆ 

Y for ಯಮ 
ನಾವೇ ಅದು 

Z for …

ಇದೆ ನಿಮಗೆ ಕೊಡ್ತಾ ಇರೋ ಹೋಮೇವರ್ಕ್-ಉ ಸ್ಟೂಡೆಂಟ್ಸ್ 
ಅರ್ಥ ಆಯ್ತಾ?

snippet.title: Chhodh Ke Na Jaa Ooh Piya (Lyrical Video) | Alka Yagnik | Sunny Deol, Tabu | Maa Tujhhe Salaam
snippet.description:
"Chhodh Ke Na Jaa Ooh Piya" is a soulful and emotional track from the movie Maa Tujhhe Salaam (2002), beautifully sung by Alka Yagnik. The song expresses a deep sense of love, longing, and heartache, as the singer pleads with her lover not to leave. With its heartfelt lyrics and Alka Yagnik’s powerful voice, this song stands out as one of the most poignant and memorable moments in the film.

Credits: 
Singer: Alka Yagnik
Music: Sajid-Wajid
Lyrics: Sameer
Movie: Maa Tujhhe Salaam
Starring: Sunny Deol, Tabu
Director: Tinu Verma
Producer: Mahendra Dhariwal
Label: Universal Music India

snippet.title: துபாய்ல கற்பனை செய்ய முடியாத ஒரு  தீவுக்கு போறோம் | Exclusive | Dubai | Chapter 1
snippet.description:
🌍 Exploring The Heart of Europe – A European Island Hidden Inside Dubai 🇦🇪

The journey begins at Al Wasl Marine Transport Station, boarding a high-speed boat to the iconic World Islands. As the boat races across the Arabian Gulf, the story of how these islands were built unfolds — a bold vision of recreating the world map in the sea.

The first stop is VOCO Monaco. From the very first step, it feels like stepping into Europe — colorful streets, unique architecture, and the surprise of Rain Street, where it drizzles even under Dubai’s bright sun.

From there, a boat ride takes you across the island clusters, passing stunning recreations of European destinations like Sweden’s floating palaces, Venice-style canals, and other themed spaces that make up The Heart of Europe. Each one reflects authentic design and atmosphere from across the continent.

The next stop is the Coral Institute — a fascinating initiative focused on marine conservation. Here, coral regeneration and marine ecosystem research are done with futuristic vision and purpose.

Then comes one of the most breathtaking highlights — the Floating Seahorse Villa, a luxurious residence with a spacious open deck above water and a serene underwater bedroom below. Seeing this kind of engineering and comfort combined in the middle of the sea is truly a once-in-a-lifetime moment.

The experience continues at the Smart Police Station (SPS) — a fully automated, contactless station. A brief conversation with the officer reveals how the system works and how it’s redefining city services.

Back at VOCO Monaco, a special Malaysian-style chicken satay is prepared by celebrity chef Vibin. As the sun begins to set, there’s time to connect with the team, relax by the beach, and take in the lively Budapest-style beach party before returning to the Dubai mainland.

This is not just a tour — it’s a cinematic journey into a future-ready European world crafted inside Dubai.

snippet.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun.

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Lyrics:
Pallavi:
Vela vela vennelantha
Meedha vaali velugunantha
Moyamante nenu entha.. Arere…
Chinni gunde unnadhentha
Haayi nimpi gaalinantha
Oodhamante oopirentha.. Arere…
Kallu rendu pusthakaalu
Bhasha leni aksharaalu
Choopulone ardhamayye.. Anni maatalu…
Mundhu leni aanavaalu
Leniponi kaaranaalu
Kotha kotha onamaalu.. Enni maayalu…
Kathalenno cheppaaru
Kavithalni raasaaru
Kaalaalu dhaataaru
Yuddhaalu chesaaru
Premalo.. Thappu ledhu premalo.. || 2 ||

Charanam 1:
Aakaasham thaakaali ani undha
Naatho raa chupisthaa aa saradhaa
Nelanthaa chuttese veelundhaa
Emundhi premisthe saripodhaa
Aha mabbulanni kommalai
Poolavaana pampithe
Aa vaana peru prema le
Dhaani ooru manamu le
Ye manasuni yemadagaku ye rujuvini.. Oh.. Anthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||

Charanam 2:
Enthunte entantaa dhooraalu
Rekkallaa ayipothe paadhaalu
Unnaayaa bandhinche dhaaraalu
Oohallo untunte praanaalu
Are ningi loni chukkale
Kindhakochi cherithe
Avi neeku edhuru nilipithe
Undipova ikkade
Jaabili itu cherenu porapaatuna ani.. Oh.. Inthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||

snippet.title: देवशयनी एकादशी स्पेशल : आज देवशयनी एकादशी की चमत्कारी कथा सुनने से सभी मनोकामना पूर्ण होती है
snippet.description:
Devshayani Ekadashi :-
आषाढ़ माह के शुक्ल पक्ष की देवशयनी एकादशी से देवों का शयनकाल शुरू हो जाएगा. इस दिन से चातुर्मास की शुरुआत हो जाती है देवशयनी एकादशी का व्रत रखने और विष्णु पूजा करने से मन शुद्ध होता है और मानसिक विकार दूर होते हैं. विधिपूर्वक देवशयनी एकादशी व्रत करने एवं कथा सुनने से पुण्य फल प्राप्त होता है. सेहत ठीक रहती है और शारीरिक कष्ट दूर होता है

#AajaAaja #JaaniDushman #SunnyDeol #AkshayKumar #UditNarayan #AlkaYagnik #AnuMalik #BollywoodHits #BollywoodSongs #ActionBollywood #SupernaturalBollywood #RomanticSongs #BollywoodClassics #HindiSongs

snippet.title: ഈ പീറപ്പെണ്ണാണോ എന്റെ അമ്മ എന്ന് സത്യൻ സാർ ചോദിച്ചു | Sathyan | Adoor Bhavani old interview
snippet.description:
ഈ പീറപ്പെണ്ണാണോ എന്റെ അമ്മ എന്ന് സത്യൻ സാർ ചോദിച്ചു | Sathyan | Adoor Bhavani | #kairalitv #kairalinews 
Adoor Bhavani (1927 – 25 October 2009) was an Indian actress in Malayalam cinema, best known for her appearance in the National Award-winning film Chemmeen (1965), directed by Ramu Kariat. She had acted in about 450 films, including Mudiyanaya Puthran, Thulabharam, Kallichellamma, and Anubhavangal Paalichakal. Her last film was K. Madhu-directed Sethurama Iyer CBI. She was also a stage actress and was associated with popular theatre group KPAC.

Bhavani was born in Adoor in Travancore.Her sister, Adoor Pankajam, was also a Malayalam film actress. Adoor Bhavani died on 25 October 2009.

snippet.title: Vetri Duraisamy வளர்த்த காளைகள், 15,000+ செம்மரங்கள் | Saidai Duraisamy Farm Visit | Exclusive
snippet.description:
#vetriduraisamy #saidaiduraisamy #pasumaivikatan #redsandal 

சென்னை மாநகராட்சியின் முன்னாள் மேயரும் அதிமுக மூத்த உறுப்பினருமான சைதை துரைசாமி விவசாயத்திலும் ஆர்வம் கொண்டவர். திருவள்ளூர் மாவட்டம் திருத்தணியில் 25 ஆண்டுகளுக்கு முன்பே 60க்கும் மேற்பட்ட ஏக்கரில் நிலம் வாங்கி அங்கே செம்மரங்களை வளர்த்து வருகிறார். அங்கே நாட்டு மாடுகள், நாய்கள், கோழிகள் மட்டுமல்லாது மறைந்த அவர் மகன் வெற்றி துரைசாமி வளர்த்து வந்த காங்கேயம் காளைகளையும் பராமரித்து வருகிறார். இந்த வீடியோவில் அதுகுறித்து பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறார்.....

snippet.title: RAVI GUPTA - ADVENTURE Stand- up Comedy Reaction!
snippet.description:
Achara & Michael react to Ravi Gupta’s hilarious take on trekking in his stand-up special “Adventure” — and we were wheezing the whole time. From clueless first-timers treating it like a walk in the park to the brutal reality of climbing actual hills, Ravi absolutely nails the pain, panic, and unexpected comedy that comes with every desi trekking trip. His expressions? Spot on. The storytelling? Too real. We couldn’t stop laughing especially when he started describing how friendship changes mid Trek. If you’ve ever been on a trek (or barely survived one), this one’s going to feel hilariously familiar. Get ready for laughs, flashbacks, and full-blown secondhand breathlessness!

Thank you to our Jamazing Patron: Krishna Venkataraman!

Be a patron for CineDesi and support more videos like this!

snippet.title: Raj Thackeray Speech Funny Punch : राज ठाकरेंच्या पंचवर Supriya Sule, Rashmi Thackeray खळखळून हसल्या
snippet.description:
The Thackeray brothers' victory rally is being held today at the NSCI Dome in Worli. Preparations are in full swing for this rally. It has been reported that only the Thackeray brothers will be on the stage at the victory rally. Their victory rally is being considered important in the backdrop of the municipal elections. The whole of Maharashtra was wondering whether the two Thackeray brothers will come together and form an alliance. Maharashtra is likely to get its answer today. The entire organization is also curious about whether the announcement of the alliance regarding the Thackeray brothers, which is in the minds of the people, will be made today or not. 

वरळीतील NSCI डोममध्ये आज ठाकरे बंधूंचा विजयी मेळावा होत आहे. या मेळाव्याची जय्यत तयारी सुरू आहे. विजयी मेळाव्याला मंचावर फक्त ठाकरे बंधू असणार अशी माहिती मिळाली आहे. महानगरपालिका निवडणुकीच्या पार्श्वभूमीवर त्यांचा हा विजयी मेळावा महत्त्वाचा मानला जात आहे. दोन्ही ठाकरे बंधू एकत्र येत युती करणार का असा प्रश्न संपूर्ण महाराष्ट्राला पडला होता. त्याचं उत्तर आज महाराष्ट्राला मिळण्याची शक्यता आहे. जनतेच्या मनातील ठाकरे बंधूंबद्दल असलेली युतीची घोषणा आज होणार की नाही याची देखील उत्सुकता संपूर्ण म आयोजन करण्यात आलं आहे.

Potato (आलू ) - 4 Nos, Boiled

Coriander leaves (हरा धनिया) 
Salt (नमक) - As Per Taste
